The all new Acorn TV app is now available! We have been hard at work to bring you a significantly improved new version of Acorn TV on iOS: Major stability improvements Enhanced navigation Brand new My Acorn TV feature listing your recently watched shows and curated watchlist Ability to favorite your top shows and find them later in My Acorn TV More playback features such as back and skip 10 seconds Enhanced search capabilities now allow you to search by cast member episode name and show title Airplay optimization Flawless iOS 11.3 support And many many bug fixes to enhance on boarding and playback
Fixed the trailers video playback bug. Several minor UI adjustments and bug fixes. Subscription terms added to the welcome screen.
New 7 Day Free Trial for new subscribers. Updated Customer Support. Added support for upcoming Chromecast feature. Improved screen scrolling. Several minor bug fixes and enhancements.

Major improvements to Recently Watched! After a Recently Watched video finishes playing the show s details screen is displayed highlighting the next episode for you to watch. Now ideally suited for easily binge watching your favorite shows! Closed Captioning support in the app s Settings has been greatly improved so that it now serves as an easy 1 step ON OFF switch. Closed Captioning has also been fixed for rewind fast forward and resume watching. Video sound is now always audible even if you have the iOS device s hardware ringer switch set to Mute Vibrate. Easily rewind 10 seconds with the video player s convenient new 10 Second Rewind button. AirPlay support has been improved in the video player. Also resolved the issue where AirPlay streaming would stop if the iOS device fell into sleep mode or locked screen. Made several optimizations and bug fixes throughout the app to improve app stability and performance.

Completely redesigned and redeveloped from the ground up to provide you with an enhanced browsing and video viewing experience! New visitors can now sign up for the 30 day free trial within the iOS app. Several new features and improvements have been added.
